     H            Y.
      ** UEXR46B ***************************************************
      *  GET NEW SHID BY MANIFEST# FROM AB3EP62                    *
      *  JW     2021.09.23                                         *
      **************************************************************
      *  CALLING SEQ.                                              *
      *                    CALL 'UEXR46B'
      *                    PARM           $NONY   4
      *                    PARM           $ORDN  10
      *                    PARM           $SHID  10
      *   IN  $NONY   4A  DELIVERY#                                *
      *       $ORDN  10A  ORDER#                                   *
      *   OUT $SHID  10A  SHIP ID                                  *
      **************************************************************
     FAB#EP62 IF  E           K        DISK
      ***********************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $ORDN  10
     C                     PARM           $SHID  10
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $SHID
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ AB#EP62                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C                     MOVELE3PRTN    LTR4    4
     C           LTR4      IFNE $NONY
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           E3ORDN    IFNE $ORDN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELE3SHID    $SHID
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
